Hi everyone. @Jean-Baptiste Vienney or I will be recording talks for this seminar, and/or sometimes the speaker may record offline if they prefer.

The default zoom link for most talks is this
If the talk is occuring at a different link that will be noted in the topc for that talk.

If you wish to add this event to your calendar, please use the export links at the bottom of this page

We may have a better organization format in the future, but worst case you should always be able to find recordings in this dropbox folder. Presently it is empty!

Have a pleasant day.
Just want to recall that the first talk will take place today (May 22) at GMT 1400 and we will use the default Zoom link :wait_one_second:
